import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-create-restaurant', templateUrl: './create-restaurant.component.html', styleUrls: ['./create-restaurant.component.css'] }) export class CreateRestaurantComponent { token = localStorage.getItem('token') user:any = localStorage.getItem('user') editData = false createOne = false constructor(){ if( this.token && JSON.parse(this.user).userType=='Owner' && JSON.parse(this.user).restaurant=='' ){ this.createOne=true } if(this.token && JSON.parse(this.user).userType=='Owner' && JSON.parse(this.user).restaurant ){ this.editData=true } } }
